Chelsea and Tottenham have held talks but Juventus have a meeting scheduled with Rijeka on Sunday.

And Turkish side Trabzonspor are also believed to have made an offer.

Defoe, meanwhile, is keen to return to England and is also wanted by Harry Redknapp at QPR but the deal may be beyond the Loftus Road club's budget.

